  <entry>
    <title>Windows 下通过 Scoop 为 VSCode 配置 clangd</title>
    <link href="https://thejiahao.github.io/posts/645e20ca"/>
    <id>https://thejiahao.github.io/posts/645e20ca</id>
    <published>2022-05-11T21:00:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2023-12-25T22:00:00.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>使用 Scoop 安装 <a href="https://clangd.llvm.org/">clangd</a> 可以自动配置环境变量和避免 VSCode 找不到 <code>#include</code>。</p><span id="more"></span><h2 id="安装方式"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#安装方式"></a> 安装方式</h2><ol><li><p>安装 <a href="https://scoop.sh/">Scoop</a></p> <pre><code class="hljs shell">Invoke-WebRequest get.scoop.sh | Invoke-Expression</code></pre></li><li><p>安装 <a href="https://winlibs.com/">Winlibs</a> 编译的 MinGW + Clang + clangd</p> <pre><code class="hljs shell">scoop install mingw-winlibs</code></pre></li><li><p>VSCode 安装 <a href="https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=llvm-vs-code-extensions.vscode-clangd">clangd</a> 扩展。</p></li></ol><div class="tag link"><a class="link-card" title="clangd - Visual Studio Marketplace" href="https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/itemsitemName=llvm-vs-code-extensions.vscode-clangd"><div class="left"><img src="https://llvm-vs-code-extensions.gallerycdn.vsassets.io/extensions/llvm-vs-code-extensions/vscode-clangd/0.1.26/1703134180510/Microsoft.VisualStudio.Services.Icons.Default" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://llvm-vs-code-extensions.gallerycdn.vsassets.io/extensions/llvm-vs-code-extensions/vscode-clangd/0.1.26/1703134180510/Microsoft.VisualStudio.Services.Icons.Default" srcset="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///////yH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw=="/></div><div class="right"><p class="text">clangd - Visual Studio Marketplace</p><p class="url">https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/itemsitemName=llvm-vs-code-extensions.vscode-clangd</p></div></a></div>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;使用 Scoop 安装 &lt;a href=&quot;https://clangd.llvm.org/&quot;&gt;clangd&lt;/a&gt; 可以自动配置环境变量和避免 VSCode 找不到 &lt;code&gt;#include&lt;/code&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
